[h3 id=Comments 
	" Comments
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"This is yet another Sonic Advance run, but it is Tails that gets his time in the spotlight! While it doesn't make use of the Ultra Dash, it also uses its fair share of glitches that gives Tails a pretty good chance at beating the game in record time. I must state that Tails' mechanics are very weird, but also interesting at the same time.
	$LF
]p
